<ab facs="#facs_159_r2l5">ſölıch ſache nıht lıeb vnd hören der nıht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / Vnd ob wır des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r2l6">her nach ıcht red hören <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> / ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r2l7">des <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> yngedenk ſein / Denn wo wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_159_r2l8">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> Oſwaldȷ </ab>
